name: Voxed Stars Spaceman 50 Edition Holder
description:
This was given to those that had collected 50 Spacemen or more by 10/31/2021 
Thank you for your time and support, you are the foundation of Voxed Stars. It's because of collectors like you that I can keep making Voxed Stars. Keep Vibin. Special shout out to Edogxx for being the first to join us on this journey. Your dedication is appreciated.
